аняемой территории.\n\n - Квартиру представляет агент Capital Mars - Вазифа.\n - ID объекта 6573.", "photos": [{"id": 2405606288, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606288-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606288-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606288-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606288-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2405606298, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606298-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606298-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606298-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606298-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2405606330, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606330-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606330-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606330-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606330-3.jpg", "isLayout": true, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2405606394, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606394-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606394-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606394-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606394-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2405606434, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606434-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606434-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606434-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606434-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2405606441, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2405606441-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "http